OL,3,CJohn Torode's ITV cooking show will
OL,4,Ccontinue to air despite BBC sacking
OL,6,FJohn Torode's ITV show 'John and
OL,7,FLisa's Weekend Kitchen', which he
OL,8,Fpresents alongside his wife Lisa
OL,9,FFaulkner, will continue to air as
OL,10,Fplanned this weekend following his BBC
OL,11,Fsacking, ITV News understands.
OL,13,FThe show, which is on its tenth
OL,14,Fseason, sees the couple invite cameras
OL,15,Finto their kitchen to teach viewers
OL,16,Frecipes they can recreate at home. The
OL,17,Fthird episode in this series is set to
OL,18,Fair at 11.40 am on Saturday.
