OL,3,CJohn Torode's ITV cooking show will
OL,4,Ccontinue to air despite BBC sacking
OL,6,FITV's decision comes after the BBC
OL,7,Ffailed to renew the contract of the TV
OL,8,Fchef from MasterChef over an upheld
OL,9,Fracism allegation.
OL,11,FTorode says he has "no recollection"
OL,12,Fof the alleged racist term he is
OL,13,Faccused of using, adding that he only
OL,14,Ffound out he had been pulled from the
OL,15,Fshow through the media.
OL,17,FThe BBC and production company Banijay
OL,18,Fcut ties with Torode on Tuesday
OL,19,Fafternoon after a report found he used
OL,20,Fan "extremely offensive" racist term.
