OL,6,FTorode took to social media to respond
OL,7,Fto the news: "Although I haven't heard
OL,8,Ffrom anyone at the BBC or Banijay - I
OL,9,Fam seeing and reading that I've been
OL,10,F'sacked' from MasterChef and I repeat
OL,11,Fthat I have no recollection of what
OL,12,FI'm accused of," he said.
OL,14,F"The enquiry could not even state the
OL,15,Fdate or year of when I am meant to
OL,16,Fhave said something wrong.
