OL,3,CJohn Torode's ITV cooking show will
OL,4,Ccontinue to air despite BBC sacking
OL,6,F"I'd hoped that I'd have some say in
OL,7,Fmy exit from a show I've worked on
OL,8,Fsince its relaunch in 2005, but events
OL,9,Fin last few days seem to have
OL,10,Fprevented that."
OL,12,FTorode confirmed on Monday night he
OL,13,Fwas the subject of an allegation of
OL,14,Fusing racist language that was upheld
OL,15,Fas part of a review into the behaviour
OL,16,Fof his co-presenter Gregg Wallace.
