OL,3,CJohn Torode's ITV cooking show will
OL,4,Ccontinue to air despite BBC sacking
OL,6,FThe report, commissioned by MasterChef
OL,7,Fproduction company Banijay and led by
OL,8,Flaw firm Lewis Silkin, found 45 out of
OL,9,F83 allegations against Wallace were
OL,10,Fsubstantiated, alongside two
OL,11,Fstandalone allegations made against
OL,12,Fother people, including one for using
OL,13,Fracist language.
OL,15,FIn a post on Instagram on Monday
OL,16,Fnight, Torode confirmed he was the
OL,17,Fperson alleged to have used racist
OL,18,Flanguage but said he had "no
OL,19,Frecollection of the incident" and was
OL,20,F"shocked and saddened" by the
OL,21,Fallegation.
